&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This is a full-time hourly position at &lt;strong&gt;$24.00&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;per hour&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You must have availability to work &lt;strong&gt;Monday through Friday&lt;/strong&gt; 6am-8pm&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A typical schedule is &lt;strong&gt;30-40 hours&lt;/strong&gt; per week&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
